==[[Lacrosse]]== {{see also|2012 NLL season|2012 MLL season}}
*May 19: [[Rochester Knighthawks]] defeat the [[Edmonton Rush]] in Rochester to win their third MILL/NLL title. *May 27: [[Northwestern Wildcats women's lacrosse|Northwestern]] defeats [[Syracuse Orange women's lacrosse|Syracuse]] 8–6 in the final of the [[2012 NCAA Division I Women's Lacrosse Championship|NCAA Women's Tournament]]. It is the Wildcats' seventh national title, all in the last eight years. *May 28: [[Loyola Greyhounds men's lacrosse|Loyola]] defeats in-state rival [[Maryland Terrapins men's lacrosse|Maryland]] 9–3 in the final of the [[2012 NCAA Division I Men's Lacrosse Championship|NCAA Men's Tournament]]. It is the first national title for the Greyhounds.
