{{Infobox sport governing body |name = Brazilian Cycling Confederation |abbrev = CBC |logo = Brazilian Cycling Confederation logo.jpg |logosize = 150px |sport = [[Bicycle racing]] |jurisdiction = National |aff = [[Union Cycliste Internationale|UCI]] |headquarters = [[Londrina]], [[Brazil]] |url = http://www.cbc.esp.br/ |countryflag = Brazil }}
The '''Brazilian Cycling Confederation''' ([[Portuguese language|Portuguese]]: ''Confederação Brasileira de Ciclismo'', '''CBC''') is the national [[sport governing body|governing body]] of [[bicycle racing|cycle racing]] in [[Brazil]].
The CBC is a member of the [[Union Cycliste Internationale|UCI]] and [[Confederacion Panamericana de Ciclismo|COPACI]].
==External links== * [http://www.cbc.esp.br/ Brazilian Cycling Confederation official website]
