'''Muktijoddha Sangsad KC'''  ({{lang-bn|মুক্তিযোদ্ধা সংসদ ক্রীড়া চক্র}}) is a [[association football|football]] club in [[Bangladesh]]. It is based in [[Dhaka]], [[Bangladesh]]. Since [[2012–13 Bangladesh Football Premier League|2012–13]] season, it has been using [[Sheikh Fazlul Haque Mani Stadium]], [[Gopalganj, Bangladesh|Gopalganj]] as its home ground.

